titles.title: A bill to extend the temporary suspension of duty on 3-Pyridinecarbonitrile, 5-[(2-cyano-4-nitrophenyl)azo]-2-[[2-(2-hydroxyethyoxy)ethyl] amino]-4-methyl-6-(phenylamino)-.

action.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 10/29/2009--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to extend the temporary suspension of duty on 3-Pyridinecarbonitrile, 5-[(2-cyano-4-nitrophenyl)azo]-2-[[2-(2-hydroxyethyoxy)ethyl] amino]-4-methyl-6-(phenylamino)-.
